    "body" : "<p>Really simple: framework. That is. All 'custom' annotations processed by frameworks using reflection. Only small scope of annotations are processed by compiler, such as <code>@Override</code>, <code>@SuppressWarnings</code>, <code>@Retention</code> and so on</p>\n"
